data.description: Huge 4 bed/1bath bungalow in a desired area with a full living room, dining room and 3 bedrooms on the main level.  There is 1 bedroom upstairs in the attic, with the potential to add a 5th bedroom and or a 2nd bathroom.  Basement is open and ready for rehab and to add a 3rd bathroom.  Nice yard, and a 2.5 garage. As-Is. Cash, Conventional or FHA 203k loans.
